  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    participant A as Computadora A<br/>(00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E)\n    participant S as Switch<br/>(Tabla MAC)\n    participant B as Computadora B<br/>(00:2B:3C:4D:5E:6F)\n    participant C as Computadora C<br/>(00:3C:4D:5E:6F:70)\n    participant D as Computadora D<br/>(00:4D:5E:6F:70:81)\n\n    Note over S: Tabla MAC vacía\n\n    Note over A,D: FASE 1: ARP Request (Broadcast)\n    \n    A->>S: ARP Request<br/>Origen: A (00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E)<br/>Destino: Broadcast (FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF)\n    \n    Note over S: Aprende: Puerto 1 → MAC de A\n    \n    S->>B: ARP Request (Flooding)\n    S->>C: ARP Request (Flooding)\n    S->>D: ARP Request (Flooding)\n    \n    Note over B,D: Solo C responde al ARP\n\n    Note over A,D: FASE 2: ARP Response\n    \n    C->>S: ARP Response<br/>Origen: C (00:3C:4D:5E:6F:70)<br/>Destino: A (00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E)\n    \n    Note over S: Aprende: Puerto 3 → MAC de C\n    \n    S->>A: ARP Response (Unicast)\n\n    Note over A,D: FASE 3: Comunicación Directa\n    \n    A->>S: Datos para C<br/>Origen: A (00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E)<br/>Destino: C (00:3C:4D:5E:6F:70)\n    \n    Note over S: Consulta tabla MAC<br/>Encuentra C en puerto 3\n    \n    S->>C: Datos (Solo puerto 3)",
