  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图来展示交换机学习MAC地址的完整过程，从ARP广播到最终的单播通信。场景是四台电脑A、B、C、D连接到一个交换机。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "Switch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先把参与者列出来：A、B、C、D四台电脑，还有中间的交换机。每台电脑需要标注MAC地址吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MAC地址",
        "参与者"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，每台电脑的MAC地址都要标清楚。A是00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E，B是00:2B:3C:4D:5E:6F，C是00:3C:4D:5E:6F:70，D是00:4D:5E:6F:70:81。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "00:1a:2b:3c:4d:5e",
        "00:2b:3c:4d:5e:6f",
        "00:3c:4d:5e:6f:70",
        "00:4d:5e:6f:70:81"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，参与者都设置好了，交换机我也标注了\"Tabla MAC\"。现在需要说明初始状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Tabla MAC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要加一个注释说明交换机一开始MAC表是空的。然后进入第一阶段：A要发ARP请求找C，但不知道C的MAC，所以发广播。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over S",
        "ARP Request",
        "broadcast",
        "ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我添加了\"Tabla MAC vacía\"的注释，然后画了A到S的ARP Request，标注了源MAC是A，目的MAC是广播地址FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "S",
        "ARP Request",
        "broadcast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "很好。接下来交换机要学习A的MAC地址，记录到端口1。然后交换机要做flooding，把ARP请求转发给B、C、D三台电脑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Puerto 1",
        "flooding",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：交换机学习A的MAC到端口1的注释，以及S到B、S到C、S到D的三条flooding箭头，都标注为ARP Request。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "flooding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里需要说明一下，虽然B、C、D都收到了ARP请求，但只有C会响应，因为请求的是C的IP地址。B和D会静默丢弃。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "ARP Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "了解了，我加一个注释\"Solo C responde al ARP\"来说明这一点。现在进入第二阶段ARP响应？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "ARP Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第二阶段是ARP Response。C现在知道A的MAC了，所以直接单播回复给A，不再广播。响应经过交换机。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "A",
        "ARP Response",
        "unicast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画了C到S的ARP Response，标注源MAC是C（00:3C:4D:5E:6F:70），目的MAC是A（00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "S",
        "A",
        "ARP Response",
        "unicast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这时候交换机又要学习——把C的MAC记录到端口3。然后交换机查表，知道A在端口1，所以直接单播转发给A。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Puerto 3",
        "Tabla MAC",
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了交换机学习C到端口3的注释，然后画了S到A的ARP Response单播箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "A",
        "Puerto 3",
        "unicast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在进入第三阶段：直接通信。A要给C发数据，这次不需要广播了，直接发给交换机。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "datos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画了A到S的数据帧，标注\"Datos para C\"，源MAC是A，目的MAC是C。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "S",
        "datos",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "交换机收到后查MAC表，发现C在端口3，所以只从端口3转发出去，不会flooding了。这是关键——体现交换机的智能转发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Tabla MAC",
        "Puerto 3",
        "solo puerto 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了交换机查表的注释\"Consulta tabla MAC, Encuentra C en puerto 3\"，然后画了S到C的数据传输，标注\"Solo puerto 3\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "C",
        "datos",
        "solo puerto 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我需要确认一下阶段划分是否清晰。第一阶段ARP请求、第二阶段ARP响应、第三阶段直接通信，这三个阶段都要明确标注出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
