    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到ARP Request的标注里，广播地址写的是小写的ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff，但规范通常是大写FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF，需要统一吗？",
